  "title": "Sales Engineer",
  "description": "<p>Key Responsibility</p><ul><li><p>Prospect and generate new leads </p></li><li><p>Develop and maintain relationships with existing and potential customers</p></li><li><p>Regularly conduct seminars, product demonstrations and technical presentations to customers and prospects</p></li><li><p>Develop sales proposals and negotiate contracts</p></li><li><p>Meet or exceed monthly and annual sales targets</p></li><li><p>Meet or exceed weekly sales activities targets</p></li><li><p>Collaborate with the marketing team to develop and implement effective sales strategies</p></li><li><p>Monitor industry trends and provide feedback to the sales and marketing teams</p></li><li><p>Attend trade shows and industry events to network and generate leads</p></li></ul>",
